     <div id="content">
		<div class="row">
			<div class="large-12 columns">
				<div class="larger-4 large-offset-4"><h2>FreshersPool</h2></div>
				<div class="larger-4">
				</div>
			</div>
		</div> 
		<div class="row">
		<div class="large-12">
			<p class="data-big">
				We connect the innovative and deserving freshers to the Companies which are looking for talent to prosper.
			</p>
		</div>
		</div>
		<div class="row">
			<div class="large-12 columns">
				<div class="large-5 columns">
					<div class="panel">
					  <h3>Freshers</h3>
					  <p>If you are a fresher looking for a job! Click below</p>
					  <input class="fresher-btn button small radius" type="submit" value="I'm a Fresher" />
					</div>
				</div>
				<div class="large-5 columns">
					<div class="panel">
					  <h3>Recruiters</h3>
					   <p>If you are a Recruiter looking to hire a Fresher! Click below</p>
					   <input class="recruiter-btn button small radius" type="submit" value="I'm a Recruiter" />
					</div>
				</div>
			</div>
		</div>

		<div class="row">
			<div class="large-12 columns">
				
				
			</div>
		
		</div>
	</div> 
	<div id="content2">
		<div class="row">
			<div class="large-12 columns"><h1>Freshers</h1></div>
		</div>
		<div class="row">
			<div class="large-12 columns">
			<div class="large-8 columns">
				<p>Freshers plays a vital role in supporting successful completion of the projects. Fresherpool.com has understood this need and supports clients to develop and nurture resources considering the project requirement. We provide freshers to corporates who are ready with all the three vital dimensions – Technical , Behavioral , Role.</p>
			</div>
				
				<div class="large-4 small-12 columns">
				<div class="panel">
					<form class="sign-form" action="@Href("~/Home/Authenticate")" id="SignInForm" method="post">
		           		<h3>Fresher Login</h3>
		           		<div id="loginf">
                               <label>User Name :</label>
		                           @Html.TextBox("username")
		           		</div>
		           		<div>
                               <label>Password :</label>
		                           @Html.Password("password")	
		           		</div>
		           		<div>
		           			<input id="loginf-btn" class="button radius" type="submit" value="Log in" /> <br />
		           			<a data-reveal-id="fresherModal" data-reveal-ajax="CA_PersonalData/Create" >New User? Register</a>
		           			<div id="fresherModal" class="reveal-modal large"></div>
		           		</div>
		           	</form>
		           	</div>
				</div>
			</div>
		</div>
		<div class="row">
			<div class="large-12 columns">
				<div class="large-4 columns">
					<h3>Technical Dimension</h3>
					<p>Determines the ability to handle present technology and adaptation to emerging trends.</p>
				</div>
				<div class="large-4 columns">
					<h3>Behavioural Dimension</h3>
					<p>Creates a conductive working environment with right attitude.</p>
				</div>
				<div class="large-4 columns">
					<h3>Role Dimension</h3>
					<p>Facilitates the performance of daily responsibilities as the role definition</p>
				</div>
			</div>					
		</div>
		<div class="row">
			<div class="large-12 columns">
			<h3>On-campus Recruitment solutions</h3>
			<ul>
				<li>How prepared are you for a Campus Recruitment Drive?</li>
				<li>Do you have a mechanism to identify the right Campus, Region wise and Domain wise?</li>
				<li>Are you facing difficulty in assessing the candidates?</li>

			</ul>

				<h3>Did You Know</h3>
                <ul>
				<li>Only 1 University in India offers ME/M.Tech in Cloud computing</li>
				<li>Only 20 colleges in India offers BE/Btech in Textile Engineering</li>
				<li>Only 43 colleges in India offer Aerospace Engineering</li>
				<li>Check out our unique Campus Search and know your campuses better.</li>
                </ul>
			</div>
		</div>

		

	</div>
	<div id="content3">
		<div class="row">
			<div class="large-12 columns"><h1>Employers</h1></div>
		</div>
		<div class="row">
			<div class="large-12 columns">
			<div class="large-8 columns">
				<p>Newly recruited staff plays a vital role in supporting successful completion of the projects. fresherpool has understood this need and supports clients to develop and nurture resources considering the project requirement. We design and develop Graduate Hiring  plans for the organizations and execute the same on turn-key basis. We are preferred vendors for conducting Induction level training programs for most of our clients including IBM, Amdocs, DELL, Tieto, Tech Mahindra, Tata Honeywell, Bank of America, Syntel to name a few.  </p>
				<p>Fresherpool.com. MMS business unit delivers recruitment and career services to organizations and individuals across the employment lifecycle. Skilled resources and Organizational market standing in the short duration Fresherpool.com-MMS has established as qualified staffing solution providers and one of the leading supplier of Permanent or Contract staff.</p>
				<p>We are specialist in providing high caliber and experienced Technical/Management Professionals optimally matching with the Clients' job requirements in all disciplines at all levels of hierarchy.</p>
			</div>
				
				<div class="large-4 small-12 columns">
				<div class="panel">                    
                    <form class="sign-form" action="@Href("~/Home/AuthenticateRecruiter")" id="SignInForm1" method="post">
	            		<h3>Employer Login</h3>
	            		<div>
                               <label>User Name :</label>
		                           @Html.TextBox("username")
		           		</div>
		           		<div>
                               <label>Password :</label>
		                           @Html.Password("password")	
		           		</div>
	            		<div>
	            			<input id="loginr-btn"  class="button radius" type="submit" value="Log in" /> <br />
		           			<a data-reveal-id="recruiterModal" data-reveal-ajax="EM_EmployerData/Create" >New User? Register</a>
		           			<div id="recruiterModal" class="reveal-modal large"></div>
	            		</div>
	            	</form>
	            	</div>


				</div>
			</div>
